{"tid":1589783,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[海外文宣］突發Pepe 成功登上少女峰","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:36:07.000Z","uid":321928,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"14f3201c53cbb7005c7760a1969e4c7eb220ee26","tid":1589783,"uid":321928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"繼富士山巴 白朗峰巴<br />\n同一眾兄弟係世界各地遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n為左兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\nPepe決定係瑞士少女峰山頂遍地開花<br />\n雖然途中好多大陸人鬧pepe傻B、港獨<br />\n但興幸仲有支持Pepe既人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hULCCoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhULCCoT.jpg&h=a3672bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPepe仲去埋聯合國總部<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BcLfo48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBcLfo48.jpg&h=ce4111f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，決一不可<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPjoxXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPjoxXH.jpg&h=99bc6297&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09095ff07a14df8b1482372d5f5d1c3239206c8d","tid":1589783,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"ee7acca344cbedc89f7a75bf14c3615682469fb5","tid":1589783,"uid":808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靚到嘩一聲"},{"pid":"6fc29644547a001bf456429ffdbaa0fa52371cb2","tid":1589783,"uid":322637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆